Usage: checkFPlan [-help] [-keep_out_distance <value>] [-outFile <fileName>]
                  [-reportUtil]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-keep_out_distance <value>       # specifies keep out distance for TSV check.
                                 # This option is only used when -checkTypes
                                 # tsv (float, optional)
-outFile <fileName>              # report file name (string, optional)
-reportUtil                      # report core utilization (bool, optional)